OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FA mother and daughter from Wiltshire
OL,8,Fhave been sentenced for their part in
OL,9,Fthe killing of a man with whom they
OL,10,Fhad both been in a relationship.
OL,12,FRaymond Groves, 48, from Hartcliffe,
OL,13,Fwas found dead at Letishia Goodwin's
OL,14,Fhome in Strawberry Fields, Easterton,
OL,15,FWiltshire, in July 2024. He had been
OL,16,Fstabbed multiple times.
OL,18,FSalisbury Crown Court heard Goodwin
OL,19,Fmade a 999 call, saying she had been
OL,20,Fout of her house and had left her
OL,21,Fmother there.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
