FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FGoodwin's mother, Helen Shakespeare,
OL,8,Ftold police who arrived at the scene
OL,9,Fthat she had stabbed Groves after he
OL,10,F"went at me."
OL,12,FBut an investigation showed neither
OL,13,Fwoman had carried out the attack.
OL,15,FInstead, it was Goodwin's new partner,
OL,16,FAnthony Hillier. He had lain in wait
OL,17,Ffor Groves to arrive. Hillier's DNA
OL,18,Fwas found on the murder weapon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,F"I've been in the police 21 years, and
OL,8,Fthis is the first murder like this
OL,9,Fthat I've ever dealt with," said Det
OL,10,FCh Insp Deb Hatch of Wiltshire Police.
OL,12,F"I think it goes to show how
OL,13,Fcalculated humans can be. They won't
OL,14,Fstop at anything. In terms of
OL,15,FLetishia, her view of Raymond was she
OL,16,Fhated him, and that was what was
OL,17,Fdriving her."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FThe court was told Shakespeare had
OL,8,Fbeen in a relationship with Groves for
OL,9,Fseveral years from 2012, but they had
OL,10,Fsplit up, remaining in a circle of
OL,11,Ffriends.
OL,13,FIt is unclear when his relationship
OL,14,Fwith Goodwin happened, but from
OL,15,FNovember 2023, it was clear Goodwin
OL,16,F"hated Raymond."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FThe trial was told there had been a
OL,8,Fplan for the mother, Shakespeare, to
OL,9,Fcarry out the attack a few days
OL,10,Fearlier, but she didn't go through
OL,11,Fwith it.
OL,13,F"It's at that point then that, Hillier
OL,14,Fdecided that he was going to do it,"
OL,15,Fsaid DCI Hatch.
OL,17,F"And the interaction between him and,
OL,18,FLetishia was that they were the
OL,19,Fdriving force. They were in control of
OL,20,Fwhat was going to happen."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FSalisbury Crown Court heard
OL,8,FShakespeare and Goodwin had lured
OL,9,FGroves to the house. Detectives
OL,10,Fbelieve they wanted to scare him, but
OL,11,FHillier went further.
OL,13,FThe trio were convicted of a variety
OL,14,Fof offences.
OL,16,FAnthony Hillier, 35 of Brooklands,
OL,17,FRoyal Wootton Basset, was found guilty
OL,18,Fof murder. He was sentenced to life in
OL,19,Fprison with a minimum term of 26 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FShakespeare, 55, of Strawberry Fields,
OL,8,FEasterton, was found guilty of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter but not guilty of murder.
OL,10,FShe was sentenced to five years in
OL,11,Fprison.
OL,13,FGoodwin, 31, of Strawberry Fields,
OL,14,FEasterton, was deemed unfit to plea
OL,15,Fbut was found guilty of participating
OL,16,Fin the murder and was given a hospital
OL,17,Forder following a trial.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
