OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDet Ch Insp Deb Hatch added:
OL,13,F"Raymond's death was the result of a
OL,14,Fbrutal and sustained attack, and
OL,15,Ftoday's verdicts reflect the gravity
OL,16,Fof the actions taken by those
OL,17,Fresponsible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
