FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783676987
OL,3,CTrio sentenced for their part in
OL,4,Ckilling man, 48, following love
OL,5,Ctriangle
OL,7,F"I want to pay tribute to the
OL,8,Fdedication of every officer and staff
OL,9,Fmember involved, and to Raymond's
OL,10,Ffamily, who have shown remarkable
OL,11,Fstrength throughout an incredibly
OL,12,Fdifficult process.
OL,14,F"The thoughts of all those on the
OL,15,Finvestigation team remain with his
OL,16,Ffamily at this difficult time."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
